se via the DreamHost control panel � or command line if you are happier. Make a note of the setup details: host, db name, username and password.</block><block font-size="10.0pt" space-before.optimum="1em" space-before.minimum="0.8em" space-before.maximum="1.2em">vi localconfig<block/>[Update group and MySQL settings.]</block></flow></page-sequence></root>